messages.content: Continue this song: wish we could turn back time...
to the good old days, when our momma sang us to sleep but now we're stressed out.
What's the name of the song and who sings it?
The name of the song is "Stressed Out" and it is sung by the band Twenty One Pilots.
I thought that's The Chainsmokers, but cool :)
I apologize for the confusion. You are correct that "Stressed Out" is not by The Chainsmokers, but rather by Twenty One Pilots. Thank you for bringing that to my attention.
Another song by twenty one pilots that I wish you could continue: No I don't know which way I'm going
But I can hear my way around...
Another one: "cause I can't help falling in..."
love with you. Shall I stay? Would it be a sin? If I can't help falling in love with you. These are the lyrics from the song "Can't Help Falling In Love" by Elvis Presley.
